<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reserva Nacional Selva Esmeralda - Ministerio del Ambiente</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-green: #0b4a3a;
            --emerald: #50c878;
            --alert-red: #b22222;
            --bg-sand: #f4f1ea;
            --text-gray: #333;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-sand);
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background-color: var(--primary-green);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--emerald);
        }

        .gov-banner {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .hero {
            background-color: #000;
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url('https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1MAO83-D97JncfT6a-olrg9ocAHbtK1kY&sz=w1200');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.6rem; 
            font-style: italic; 
            font-weight: normal; 
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); 
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .alert-box {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid var(--alert-red);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: -40px auto 30px;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .alert-box h2 {
            color: var(--alert-red);
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .carousel-container {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px; 
            position: relative; 
        }
        .carousel {
            display: flex;
            overflow-x: auto;
            scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
            gap: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            scrollbar-width: thin;
            scrollbar-color: var(--primary-green) var(--bg-sand);
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        .carousel::-webkit-scrollbar { height: 6px; }
        .carousel::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
        .carousel::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background-color: rgba(11, 74, 58, 0.4); border-radius: 4px; }
        
        .carousel-card {
            scroll-snap-align: center;
            flex: 0 0 85%;
            max-width: 400px;
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--primary-green);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .carousel-card img { width: 100%; height: 250px; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
        .carousel-card .caption { padding: 12px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--primary-green); font-weight: bold; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--emerald); }

        .carousel-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 45%; 
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            background-color: rgba(11, 74, 58, 0.7); 
            color: white;
            border: none;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 10;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .prev-btn { left: -15px; }
        .next-btn { right: -15px; }

        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-bottom: 4px solid var(--primary-green); }
        .card h3 { color: var(--primary-green); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--emerald); padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0; }

        .footer { background-color: #222; color: #888; text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 60px; }
        .stamp { border: 3px double var(--alert-red); color: var(--alert-red); display: inline-block; padding: 5px 15px; transform: rotate(-5deg); font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0; }

        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; }
            .hero { padding: 60px 15px; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: center 25%; }
            .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; }
            .alert-box { margin-top: -20px; }
            .carousel-card { flex: 0 0 90%; } 
            .carousel-btn { width: 35px; height: 35px; font-size: 1.2rem; }
            .prev-btn { left: 5px; }
            .next-btn { right: 5px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div class="gov-banner">Ministerio del Ambiente - Gobierno de la Amazonía</div>
    <h1>Reserva Nacional Selva Esmeralda (RNSE)</h1>
</header>

<div class="hero">
    <p>"Preservando el último misterio de la Amazonía"</p>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="alert-box">
        <h2>⚠️ AVISO CRÍTICO DE ACCESO</h2>
        <p>El acceso al público general está estrictamente <strong>PROHIBIDO</strong>. Solo se permite el ingreso a personal científico acreditado previa aprobación del Ministerio del Ambiente.</p>
        <div class="stamp">ACCESO RESTRINGIDO</div>
    </div>

    <section>
        <h2 style="border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-green); padding-left: 15px; font-size: 1.3rem;">Registros Visuales (Archivos Fotográficos)</h2>
        <div class="carousel-container">
            <button class="carousel-btn prev-btn">❮</button>
            <div class="carousel" id="photoCarousel">
                <div class="carousel-card"><img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1xvIqkqIPAKFC1JUuooqiflvsjwCAiwNS&sz=w800"><div class="caption">The Colossal Emerald Stag</div></div>
                <div class="carousel-card"><img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1VkYl5CUUkhbWBLQOHWdxQyapIBuY1NH2&sz=w800"><div class="caption">The Río Esmeralda</div></div>
                <div class="carousel-card"><img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1MR9eGLwHAr4Ot1dy2QLrlaHb2mLLCM5S&sz=w800"><div class="caption">Ranger 'K'atun' on Patrol</div></div>
                <div class="carousel-card"><img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1j98fzuj4-JEPG13u1HWPgc23i9nZhu_W&sz=w800"><div class="caption">CETJ Field Station: Sector 4</div></div>
                <div class="carousel-card"><img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1o_pI8UQMfNtnZyTaEaH0Y4992X51EWYr&sz=w800"><div class="caption">Unmapped Ruins: The Jaguar Glyph</div></div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-btn next-btn">❯</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 style="border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-green); padding-left: 15px; font-size: 1.3rem;">Instalaciones de Investigación Especializada</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card"><h3>CETJ</h3><p><strong>Centro de Estudios Telepáticos del Jaguar:</strong> Monitoreo de campos bio-eléctricos y comunicación no verbal.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>PANC 'Visitantes'</h3><p><strong>Plataforma de Aterrizaje No Convencional:</strong> Puerto de enlace para fenómenos aéreos no identificados.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Gran Sumidero</h3><p><strong>Fosa de Anomalía Gravitatoria:</strong> Zona de exclusión para la recuperación de objetos perdidos.</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    <p>© 1992-2026 Reserva Nacional Selva Esmeralda | Dirección de Conservación de la Biodiversidad</p>
    <p>Coordenadas: 3°51'24"S 70°42'59"W | Sistema de Vigilancia Activo</p>
</div>

<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
        const carousel = document.getElementById('photoCarousel');
        const prevBtn = document.querySelector('.prev-btn');
        const nextBtn = document.querySelector('.next-btn');
        function getScrollAmount() {
            const card = document.querySelector('.carousel-card');
            return card ? card.offsetWidth + 15 : 300;
        }
        nextBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            const maxScrollLeft = carousel.scrollWidth - carousel.clientWidth;
            if (Math.ceil(carousel.scrollLeft) >= maxScrollLeft - 5) {
                carousel.scrollTo({ left: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
            } else {
                carousel.scrollBy({ left: getScrollAmount(), behavior: 'smooth' });
            }
        });
        prevBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            if (Math.floor(carousel.scrollLeft) <= 5) {
                carousel.scrollTo({ left: carousel.scrollWidth, behavior: 'smooth' });
            } else {
                carousel.scrollBy({ left: -getScrollAmount(), behavior: 'smooth' });
            }
        });
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>
